<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870602-0017 </DOCNO><HL> Financing Business:Audiovox Corp.</HL><DD> 06/02/87</DD><SO>  </SO><IN> VOXINITIAL STOCK OFFERINGS (INI)STOCK MARKET, OFFERINGS (STK) </IN><TEXT>   AUDIOVOX CORP. sold 2,525,000 Class A common shares at $16 each in an initial offering. Of the total, 2.2 million were sold by the company and the rest by shareholders. Company proceeds will be used to reduce short-term obligations. Based in Hauppauge, N.Y., Audiovox markets automotive products, such as sound equipment, cellular telephones and other accessories. Donaldson, Lufkin andamp; Jenrette Securities Corp. led the underwriting group. </TEXT></DOC>